radiographic_examinations.findings: Placement of a right IJ catheter that extends to the lower portion of the SVC. A curvilinear line projected over the outer aspect of the mid portion of the right lung, characteristics of a skin fold, but pneumothorax cannot be definitely excluded.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: In comparison with the earlier study of this date, there has been placement of a right IJ catheter.
